verbose_text: In absence of PEI, the cell viability of GA@CP treated HeLa cells was much higher than that of GAI@CP, which could be explained that the " proton sponge effect " of PEI promoted the drug escape from endo / lysosome and accelerate tumor cell apoptosis.
